-Williams </b>estimated that the WNBA currently makes about $60 million a y=
ear from the NBA=E2=80=99s media rights package.<br/><br/>More than a quart=
er-century later, amid the heights of <b>Caitlin</b>sanity, the WNBA is dra=
wing large enough TV audiences to justify
negotiating on its own. But the NBA likes having the WNBA as part of its pi=
